{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B39ThemeControlItemComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","symbolKind":"class"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for components with a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"control item"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSCheckboItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011ControlItemB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for control-item-layout-based component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the control-item-layout-based component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMinHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._500 }","","        override var colorBgFocus: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.contentDefault }","","        override var spaceRowGap: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineTall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider: ControlItemComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(controlItem: CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(controlItem: CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let controlItemComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let controlItemComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.10.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:opacities:dimensions:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/opacities","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/sizeIcon","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentatio